### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/pets
@userEmail = user@example.com

### 1. Crear mascota - Firu (Perro)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Firu",
  "type": "Perro",
  "userEmail": "{{userEmail}}"
}

### 2. Crear mascota - Kuro (Gato)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kuro",
  "type": "Gato",
  "userEmail": "{{userEmail}}"
}

### 5. Obtener todas las mascotas de user@example.com
GET {{baseUrl}}?userEmail={{userEmail}}

### 6. Obtener todas las mascotas de otro@example.com
GET {{baseUrl}}?userEmail=otro@example.com

### 7. Obtener mascota por ID = 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### 8. Obtener mascota por ID = 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/2

### 9. Eliminar mascota por ID = 1
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1